          <!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="body text" --> <h1>Operations and Premises Committee</h1> <p><strong>Chair:&nbsp; </strong><strong>Dr Lewis Griffin (Director of Premises) (<a href="mailto:P.Rounce@cs.ucl.ac.uk">l.griffin@cs.ucl.ac.uk</a>)</strong><strong> &amp; Prof David Jones (Director of Services) (d.jones@cs.ucl.ac.uk</strong><strong>) </strong></p> <p><strong>Secretary: </strong> JJ Giwa (Departmental Administrator - Facilities Management and Operations) <a href="mailto:j.giwa@cs.ucl.ac.uk">j.giwa@cs.ucl.ac.uk</a></p> <p><strong>Minutes Secretary:</strong>&nbsp; Patricia Fenoy (Departmental Office Administrator) <span class="style1 style2">p.fenoy@cs.ucl.ac.uk</span></p> <p><strong>Role:</strong> This committee provides advice, oversight and coordination of the strategic and operational management of the department&#x2019;s day-to-day operations, health, safety and security issues, and premises.</p> <p><strong>Frequency of Meeting:</strong>&nbsp; Quarterly </p> <p><b>Membership:</b></p> 
          <ul> 
           <li>Director of Services &#x2013; Chair - David Jones</li> 
           <li>Director of Premises &#x2013; Chair - Lewis Griffin </li> 
           <li> Dept Administrator (Facilities Management and Operations) - Secretary - JJ Giwa</li> 
           <li>Departmental Manager - Jill Saunders</li> 
           <li>Departmental Office Administrator - Patricia Fenoy </li> 
           <li>Operations and Premises staff representative - Kyle Jamieson</li> 
           <li>Research staff/student representatives - Muhammad Hussain, Malcolm Reynolds and Thomas Stone</li> 
           <li>Taught programme student representative - Saqib Kakvi (MSc ISec - 2009/10) </li> 
           <li>Technical Services Group - Denis Timm, Dave Twiselton, David Swapp</li> 
           <li>Health &amp; Safety - Dave Twiselton</li> 
           <li> Academic staff - Mark Handley </li> 
           <li>Environmental Responsibility Co-ordinator - Lewis Griffin</li> 
